              <div class="intro">
                  <h4 class="text-center">Welcome To</h4>
                  <h1 class="text-center">MANDAR EDUCATION SOCIETY</h1>
                  <p class="text-center">
                    Konkan is a most picturesque yet most backward
                    region of coastal Maharashtra.The youth of
                    Konkan region was deprived of technical
                    education for years. It was Mr. Rajaram Shinde's
                    concern and vision to enable this youth with some
                    kind of technical education.He bravely ventured and
                    started an institute in 1983,which is today catering
                    to about 2500 students,giving technical education.
                    Mandar Education Society campus includes the
                    institutes of Management,Engineering, Polytechnic,
                    B.Ed,Pharmacy and many more.The MES Institute
                    always leading towards the Technology.
                  </p>
